### Create a new user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "john_doe",
  "password": "password123",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "phone": "+33123456789",
  "age": 30
}

### Get all users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users

### Get user by UUID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/{{USER_UUID}}

### Create an account for the user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/accounts?userUuid={{USER_UUID}}&currency=EUR

### Get account by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/{{ACCOUNT_ID}}

### Get all accounts for a user
GET http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/user/{{USER_UUID}}

### Deposit into account
POST http://localhost:8080/api/transactions/deposit?accountId={{ACCOUNT_ID}}&amount=1000&description=InitialDeposit

### Withdraw from account
POST http://localhost:8080/api/transactions/withdraw?accountId={{ACCOUNT_ID}}&amount=200&description=ATMWithdrawal

### Create a second user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "jane_doe",
  "password": "password456",
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "phone": "+33987654321",
  "age": 28
}

### Create account for second user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/accounts?userUuid={{USER2_UUID}}&currency=EUR

### Transfer between accounts
POST http://localhost:8080/api/transactions/transfer?fromAccountId={{ACCOUNT_ID}}&toAccountId={{ACCOUNT2_ID}}&amount=150&description=Payment

### Get account balance
GET http://localhost:8080/api/transactions/account/{{ACCOUNT_ID}}/balance

### Create an exchange
POST http://localhost:8080/api/exchanges?accountId={{ACCOUNT_ID}}&from=EUR&to=USD&rate=1.1&amount=100

### Get exchanges for account
GET http://localhost:8080/api/exchanges/account/{{ACCOUNT_ID}}
